Project Dependencies:

Node.js

    To install node.js on Mac, run:
    $ brew install node

    To instal Nodejs on Linux, run:
    $ curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_6.x | sudo -E bash -
    $ sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

npm

    To install npm on Linux, run:
    $ sudo apt-get install -y npm

nginx

    To install nginx on Linux, run:
    $ sudo apt-get install -y nginx

===============================================================================

Configuring the environment:

Pull the required Javascripts:
$ npm install

Configure nginx
$ sudo ./config/webserver.sh

===============================================================================

Operating the application:

To start the site, run the following from the project root directory:
$ npm start

To view the map, visit the following URL:
localhost

